        Find Your Perfect Pair of Shoes on Myntra

        Step into a world of style and comfort with Myntra’s extensive collection of footwear. Whether you're looking for high-performance running shoes, trendy sneakers, or classic formal shoes, Myntra has the perfect pair for every occasion. From active days to casual outings, explore shoes that seamlessly blend fashion and function. Shop top brands and experience footwear designed for durability, comfort, and all-day wearability.

        The Best Footwear for Men, Women, and Children

        Complete your outfit with the ideal pair of shoes. For formal occasions, style your suit with elegant brown formal shoes. Heading to work? Impress your colleagues with a polished look featuring olive green trousers, a white and green checked shirt, and a charcoal grey dinner jacket. Pair this outfit with black lace-up formal shoes for a refined touch. Add a statement watch to leave a lasting impression.

        For casual meetings, opt for capris with stylish sandals and a striped black-and-white T-shirt. Pair this with a bold red leather bag for a professional yet trendy vibe. Planning a weekend trip? Combine ruffled tops with low-rise denim and canvas shoes to showcase your laid-back sense of style. Don't forget adorable pink canvas booties with cartoon prints for your little ones to keep them cozy and chic!

        Sporty and Stylish with Sneakers

        Sneakers are the perfect blend of sporty and stylish. Enjoy a game of basketball with friends in khaki shorts and a light blue T-shirt, accessorized with blue sneakers for a pop of color. For early morning jogs, a pair of crimson running shoes with padded soles offers superior comfort and support. Pair them with black cycling shorts and a white racerback top for a sleek and functional look.

        Stay Fit While Looking Fabulous

        Outdoor activities and picnics call for a blend of fashion and comfort. Pair above-the-knee blue shorts with a lemon-yellow floral T-shirt for a cheerful, casual vibe. Slip into flat tan bellies for an effortless style. If you’re hitting the gym, step up your fitness game with lime-green gym shoes that provide exceptional grip for high-performance workouts.         FAQ

        What shoes to wear with kurta?

        Kurta can be styled with both formal and casual footwear.

      • For Men - For a traditional occasion, you can wear sandals, loafers, and leather sandals to complete your look. For casual attire, you can pair your kurtas with jeans or trousers and then wear casual shoes, flip flops, sports sandals, or slip-ons to go with it.
      • For Women - For a traditional look, you can wear sandals, juttis, heels, and kolhapuri chappals with kurtas. For a more casual look, you can wear slip-ons, one-toe flats, or casual shoes.
      • For Kids - Kids can sport smart sandals for casual events and loafers for a more traditional look.

        • What types of shoes are for a party?

        For a party, you should be wearing shoes that are comfortable as well as matching your outfit so they can complement your overall look. 

      • For Men - If you are wearing formal attire, then formal shoes and loafers will go the best with it. If you are wearing a casual outfit, then slip-ons, sandals, or casual shoes will be a good choice for footwear. 
      • For Women - Women can wear heels, embellished flats to a party depending upon the outfit. For a more quirky look, women can also experiment with funky and colourful sneakers.
      • For Kids - Sneakers, sports shoes, slip-ons, ballerinas are the best to wear for parties.

        • Which are the top 5 shoe types used most?

      • For Men - Formal shoes, sneakers, sports shoes, loafers, and slip-ons are the most used.
      • For Women - Heels, flats, ballerinas, sneakers, and stilettos are some of the most used shoes.
      • For Kids - Sneakers, slip-ons, and ballerinas are the shoe types used mostly.
